### Create new book
POST http://localhost:3000/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Test Book",
    "author": "64c2f456a8c09aec3406ff78",
    "isbn": "1234567890",
    "publishYear": 2023,
    "genre": ["Fiction", "Mystery"],
    "pages": 300,
    "publisher": "Test Publisher",
    "language": "English",
    "inStock": true
}

